downloadDescription: Provides technical information about Xbox One P2P behavior to address possible configuration issues.
detailsSection: The primary purpose of this document is provide technical information about Xbox One P2P behavior, so that network operators and network equipment manufacturers can address possible configuration issues and ensure end-users have a positive experience.
installInstructionSection:
• To start the download, click the Download button, and then do one of the following:
    • To start the download immediately, click Open.
    • To copy the download to your computer for viewing at a later time, click Save.
    • To cancel the download, click Cancel.
